<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.4">
<l>nilavoṭu veyiṉila virucuṭarum</l>
<l>ulakamu muyirkaḷu muṇṭorukāl</l>
<l>kalaitaru kuḻaviyi ṉuruviṉaiyāy</l>
<l>alaikaṭa lālilai vaḷarntavaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who slept on a banyan leaf in the billowing sea one time,</l>
<l>Taking the form of an infant who bestows splendor,</l>
<l>Having consumed the world and [its] creatures,</l>
<l>Along with the two orbs, which radiate sunshine and moonlight,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
